name: Cactebral
printed_effect:
When an opponent activates a Counter Rune
you can Disenchant {earth} from this Cactebral
in order to Negate that Rune. When a player
Casts Sandstorm you can Special Ascend this
Cactebral to Cactebrum from your hand or deck.
